# Day 8 – Date Functions

## Topics Covered

- CURRENT_DATE
- CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
- DATE()
- STRFTIME()
- JULIANDAY()

### Example

Current Date

```sql
SELECT CURRENT_DATE;
```

Current Timestamp

```sql
SELECT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP;
```

Extract Year

```sql
SELECT STRFTIME('%Y',order_date)
FROM Orders;
```

Difference between dates

```sql
SELECT JULIANDAY('2026-07-20')-
JULIANDAY('2026-07-10');
```

